'''Star Destroyer White''' was the name given to the pigmentation of paint that was applied to the hulls of [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyers]] in [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] service. It was the only color of paint that was produced in enough quantities to be reasonably-priced for applying to [[Imperial II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial II''-class Star Destroyers]]. [[Booster Terrik]], who had wanted to paint his ''[[Errant Venture/Legends|Errant Venture]]'' red, declared that this was evidence that [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] had been out to annoy him personally all along.

